A '''birdhouse''' is used during [[bird house trapping]] on [[Fossil island]]. A birdhouse is created by placing a [[bird house (item)|regular bird house]] item on a [[bird house space]], which requires level 5 [[Hunter]]. The birdhouse can be filled with 10 low level [[hop seeds]] or [[herb seeds]], or 5 high level herb seeds. When filled with seeds, the birdhouse will passively fill with birds. After about 50 minutes, the birdhouse will be full and can be collected for [[bird nests]], [[raw bird meat]], and [[feathers]], as well as the [[clockwork]] used when crafting the item. Collecting the birdhouse awards 280 Hunter experience.

==Hunter info==
{{Hunter info
